    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable mode of transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable clear coat peeling on the hood and roof, along with a few minor door dings and light scratches from regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car starts up reliably and handles well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s a dependable daily driver that prioritizes function over form.",
