    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including some noticeable paint oxidation on the roof and hood, as well as several small dings and scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat bolster and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future to restore its original ride quality. It's a solid, honest car that offers practical transportation at an affordable price point.",
      "price": 20500.0,
