    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and it shows. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, with no signs of bolster wear or aging. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from a certified master technician. The engine bay is spotless, and the drive is tight, quiet, and powerful. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and performs as if it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 47900.0,
